column16: Lift renamed from "C03a" to "03a" to match the RFC.

Lift "03 a+b" will be divided into "03a" and "03b".  All quantities will be assigned to "03a".

Lift "C04 a+c" will be divided into "04a" and "04b".  All quantities will be assigned to "04a".
